SUMMARY:Discussion on sports journalism\, investigative reporting\, and p
 odcasting
DESCRIPTION:Steven Godfrey is a digital content creator who has worked fo
 r a variety of major media outlets over the past two decades. His work hi
 story includes co-hosting the "College Football Enquirer" podcast for Yah
 oo Sports\, working as a columnist for The Washington Post\, serving as a
  senior writer and producer for SB Nation\, and co-founding the popular c
 ollege football podcast Split Zone Duo.  Ryan Nanni\, co-host of the well
 -known college football podcast Shutdown Fullcast and a former managing e
 ditor at Vox Media\, has been at the forefront of modern digital content 
 related to college football for over a decade.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Steven Godfrey is a digital content cre
 ator who has worked for a variety of major media outlets over the past tw
 o decades. His work history includes co-hosting the "College Football Enq
 uirer" podcast for Yahoo Sports\, working as a columnist for The Washingt
 on Post\, serving as a senior writer and producer for SB Nation\, and co-
 founding the popular college football podcast Split Zone Duo.</p><p>  Rya
 n Nanni\, co-host of the well-known college football podcast Shutdown Ful
 lcast and a former managing editor at Vox Media\, has been at the forefro
 nt of modern digital content related to college football for over a decad
 e.</p>
